# CODEOWNERS - Automatic PR review assignments
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
* @your-org/core-team

# GitHub Actions workflows
.github/workflows/ @your-org/devops-team

# CI/CD scripts
/scripts/ @your-org/devops-team

# Security-sensitive files
/src/lib/security/ @your-org/security-team
/src/lib/auth/ @your-org/security-team

# Infrastructure and configuration
*.yml @your-org/devops-team
*.yaml @your-org/devops-team
*.config.* @your-org/devops-team
/supabase/ @your-org/backend-team

# Frontend components
/src/components/ @your-org/frontend-team
/src/pages/ @your-org/frontend-team

# API routes
/src/api/ @your-org/backend-team

# Documentation
*.md @your-org/docs-team
/docs/ @your-org/docs-team
